{"Sid":0,"Did":25471,"Id":"312304","Title":"尹新民（子）、尹溫壽清（母）訪談錄","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/c3492064-98f6-4dbe-98c4-16283a3aed2f/p1.63-DSC_0394尹新民.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/8e095c7c-431b-4fa7-a458-8ddf6a1c65a3/p1.63-DSC_0391.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n尹溫壽清，民國11年1月21日出生，四川省新都人。民國35年間來臺，37年離臺，民國38年再來臺。尹新民為其子，民國38年3月25日出生，出生後十天（38年4月5日）就到臺灣。出生地為上海。中正理工學院航空工程系畢業。畢業後，即到臺中漢翔工作。\n\n其父為黃埔正期班畢業，為孫立人部屬，隨著孫立人征戰緬甸，民國36年底，隨著孫立人訓練新軍，亦來臺灣擔任聯絡官。後因孫立人案而遭受牽連，多不願講述先前過往之事情，民國55年從陸軍步兵學校退伍。\n\n本次訪談含二篇訪談錄，主要價值為了解孫立人將軍來臺訓練新軍情況，並說明眷村生活情況。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"NULL","Keyword_Latitude":"NULL","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/0774E13E-9D7B-4957-AEE7-11DDD245E249","Original_Identifier":"312304","Keyword_Subject_1":"社會與政治","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"孫立人  / 眷村文化 / 黃埔新村","dates":"採訪時間 / 2019/10/16","LastUpdateTime":"2020/01/04 16:46:58","Creator":"顧超光","publisher":"","mediaType":"文件","language":"","timelines":"戰後時期 (1945~)","city":"高雄市鳳山區","address":"","lng":"","lat":"","contributors":"","contributor":"顧超光","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"高雄市政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/fd84bb00-50b6-46b1-bb70-059f5a11ce98/p1.63-DSC_0391.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/a0ba6f96-1248-4945-bc51-e91e7e66c5ce/p1.63-DSC_0394尹新民.jpg"}}